query: SELECT DISTINCT pa.agentId, COALESCE(u.name, 'NOT IN USERS') as userName, COALESCE(a.name, 'NOT IN AGENTS') as agentName FROM propertyAgents pa LEFT JOIN users u ON pa.agentId = u.id LEFT JOIN agents a ON pa.agentId = a.id ORDER BY pa.agentId;
